title: Wiring 1-2-3 Home Depot
description:
The 1-2-3 Books Wiring 1-2-3 Book 2nd Edition is a comprehensive electrical wiring guide. The book offers you detailed information and instruction on wiring projects. 1-2-3 Wiring is not only a handy source to help you avoid common mistakes, but it also will help you efficiently plan your project to save money.

   - Comprehensive book othat offers tips and advice for winting projects to assist the DIY enthusiast
   - Offers instruction on how to rewire lamps, replace plugs, reset breakers and detach old wires
   - Includes instruction on how to run cable,and add circuits
   - Can help you avoid common mistakes and select the best materials
   - Contains instructions on helping you plan your project
